	<summary>
	2/3/1993--Introduced.
Federal Transit Fair Share Act of 1993 - Amends the Federal Transit Act to base the apportionment of Federal transportation funds for certain urban and nonurban mass transportation programs on census estimates prepared by the Department of Commerce. (Currently, the apportionment is based only on the latest available Federal census.)

	</summary>
